title Authentication Sequence spa New Note

browser->server: HTTP POST https://fullstack-exampleapp.herokuapp.com/new_note_spa
server->browser: 201 Status Code

note over browser:
Send data as JSON object asyncronously through the form, with the new_note_spa method
preventing the form from refreshing the page.
end note

note over server:
Use the data JSON sent by the browser and modifies the notes list
Server status code 201, and don't ask for redirect,
and sends no further HTTP-requests.
end note
